title: Brand New Community & Up to 4 Weeks Free- PEARLAND
posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#810079', 'Inspired by You', 'Some people have found a way to enjoy it all: a satisfying career, personally fulfilling hobbies, after-hours enjoyments, and a relaxing and satisfying home life.', 'Their secret?', 'They live at this beautiful new community, the one place where all of these elements come together.', 'This community is where the city unwinds, comfortably, wonderfully, and totally.', 'Our unique blend of transitional farmhouse architecture and mid-century modern décor, combined with the soaring ceilings and open spaces, evoke relaxation.', 'The clubhouse seamlessly flows to the outside where you can spend your hours in our outdoor living room and pool area.', 'Enjoy sunsets, or even a yoga session, on the central lawn.', 'And don’t worry, we have your furry friend covered, too, with our dog park.', 'At this community, you’ll find your options are limitless.', 'Community Features:', 'Phone-enabled keyless home entry', 'Open-concept clubhouse connected to outdoor living area', 'Fully-equipped fitness center', 'Private co-working spaces and work pods', 'Indoor lounge areas', 'Central lawn with wandering creek and fountain', 'Outdoor living room including social spaces, kitchen with family-style dining area, TVs, and games', 'Pool deck with infinity-edge pool and sun shelf, private cabanas, and poolside loungers overlooking central lawn', 'Dog park with wash and watering stations', 'Grilling pavilion', '24/7 package lockers', 'Detached garages and carports', 'Uninterrupted Wi-Fi throughout community', 'Outdoor Entertainment']
